thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by LAWRENCE

author: LAWRENCE
title: LAWRENCE
text: The frame I wanted was "out of stock" when I first contacted American Frame but they told me it should be in by the end of the week and it was. I ordered it and it was on my porch on the day they said it would. It was packaged with great care and was exactly what I expected. I cut my mat, mounted the print on foam core and put it all together. My customer was delighted.
